    "# ==============================================================================\n",
    "# The Climate Cost of Urban Sprawl within Exeter-Cranbrook Corridor\n",
    "# Focus: Quantifying the Effects of Urban Sprawl in term of Urban Heat Island Intensity\n",
    "# Date: April 2026\n",
    "# =============================================================================="
   ]
  },
  {
